'''David Siegel''' is an American motion picture screenwriter and director, and part of a long-standing writing-directing team with filmmaker [[Scott McGehee]]. His films include ''[[Suture]]'' (1994), ''[[The Deep End]]'' (2001), ''[[Bee Season (film)]]'' (2005) and ''[[Uncertainty (film)]]'' (2008).
